#-       §nMiners§r §L§r§nLog
§rDay 1,
Started mining dug straight down..... The minecraft gods must love me because I reached bedrock with no complications. Hit some coal so I am in "Vanilla" Chunks. I am in the deep -,- coordinates.
#- Day 2,
All is looking good, I have made a pretty good haul, some iron redstone and coal, none of those godly diamonds.
#- Day 3,
Found a ravine while strip mining it is huge! Lets see what I can find.....
Barley anything of value lots of coal some iron and an interesting water and lava combination. Grabbed some lava from the lava lake and used it to smelt all my 
#- stone, I am going to make a little miners house down here.
#- Day 4,
This is the end, I havent eaten for a while and I am withering away. I have left all my stuff here for an adventurer like me to find. Best of luck to you I have left my stuff in this chest. 
#- 